00:57:05,661 --> 00:57:06,582
they just gave up trying.

1163
00:57:07,343 --> 00:57:08,564
And it was really depressing to see.

1164
00:57:09,145 --> 00:57:10,026
It was like they were broken,

1165
00:57:10,066 --> 00:57:11,768
and I was trying really hard not to be broken.

1166
00:57:12,528 --> 00:57:14,250
And it's possible not to be broken if you,

1167
00:57:14,951 --> 00:57:16,513
yeah, if you put your mind into it.

1168
00:57:18,285 --> 00:57:19,427
And in the end, that's what I did.

1169
00:57:19,508 --> 00:57:21,994
I kept nagging people about everything

1170
00:57:22,555 --> 00:57:23,397
to make the game better,

1171
00:57:23,778 --> 00:57:25,462
because the game is not about what I feel.

1172
00:57:25,502 --> 00:57:27,648
It's about making the coolest experience you could ever have.

1173
00:57:28,883 --> 00:57:30,464
And in the end, it got good.

